{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"feebeeb864","title":"关于领导机关应加强请示报告工作的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3d6ef327de","index":0,"year":1962,"month":8,"day":10,"articleId":"feebeeb864"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""},{"id":"maoquanji45","name":"毛泽东全集第45卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/45-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"26743e8ce0","type":"title","text":"关于领导机关应加强请示报告工作的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"feebeeb864"},{"id":"d91faa294e","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"feebeeb864"},{"id":"b0ccad3b7e","type":"paragraph","text":"此件值得一阅。中央对国内很多情况不清楚。许多领导机关封锁消息，不作论证性的报告，事前不请示，事后不报告，实行独立王国。而国外使馆消息，却如此认真而迅速。请同志们想一想，是否可以把这个十几年的老毛病改一改呢？如果再不改，那就只有执行纪律的一条路了。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"feebeeb864"}],"page":{"id":"ac590111ab","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"feebeeb864","start":0,"end":0}},"maoquanji45":{"comments":[{"id":"7a494bbbce","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"feebeeb864","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"中国驻摩洛哥大使馆党委给外交部的这个报告比较详细地介绍了阿尔及利亚民族革命斗争的基本情况、主要特点和当前领导集团内部存在的矛盾，也提出了使馆党委的一些分析和看法。"},{"id":"9c35716758","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"feebeeb864","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这个批语写在中国驻摩洛哥大使馆党委1962年8月5日关于阿尔及利亚情况和便馆的看法给外交部的报告上。"},{"id":"e618f87ba0","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"feebeeb864","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"毛泽东批语的时间手稿上写为“8月10日”，在中央工作会议文件上印为“8月11日”。"}],"contents":[{"id":"35c7e19a2f","type":"title",